<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.7">
<l>ōṭi yōṭip palpiṟappum piṟantumaṟ ṟōrteyvam</l>
<l>pāṭi yāṭip paṇintupalpaṭikāl vaḻiyē ṟikkaṇṭīr</l>
<l>kūṭi vāṉava rēttaniṉṟa tirukkuru kūrataṉu</l>
<l>ḷāṭu puṭkoṭi yāti mūrttik kaṭimai pukuvatuvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Running [and] running, being born in all the births, singing, dancing [and] humbling yourselves</l>
<l>before another god, having mounted the path of many generations, see:</l>
<l>[there is] entering into servantship to the primordial form with a dancing bird banner</l>
<l>in Tirukkurukūr where [he] stands while the celestials join [and] praise [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
